  • Classes in org.neo4j.logging used by org.neo4j.logging 
    Class Description
    AbstractLog  
    AbstractLogProvider
    An abstract LogProvider implementation, which ensures Logs are cached and reused.
    AbstractLogProvider.LogWithContext
    A log accompanied its original context, since logs may be instantiated with a modified version of the context and determining things like log level must be done on the original context.
    AssertableLogProvider  
    AssertableLogProvider.Level  
    AssertableLogProvider.LogCall

    NullLog
